
Folder : STM32F407_LIS3DSH_SPI_V1
This Folder contains a simple a c code for STM32F407 Discovery board to communicate with inbuilt LIS3DSH accelerometer Using SPI communication.

Folder : STM32F407_LIS3DSH_SPI_v2
This Folder contains a simple and necessary SPI driver declarations and functions for STM32F407 Discovery board to communicate with inbuilt LIS3DSH accelerometer.
This is not a full SPI driver, rahter a improved version of STM32F407_LIS3DSH_SPI_V1 by creating the SPI device driver.
